      "comment": "INCREDIBLE ROGUE (1) boasts a strong record this journey with 11 wins and seven minors from 29 tries. Hit the frame latest (35.54) when third at Cannington in a Grade 4/5. Looks suited and should go close. SPOTLESS WAYNE (2) goes very well at the course and distance with two wins and a placing from four starts. Recorded a neck win (29.84) in a Grade 4/5 last time at this track. Suited here and expected to run well. JAI BUBBA (8) was a winner two back then strongly fancied last time but could only manage a second (29.86) at this track. Expected to be in this for a long way. INCREDIBLE LORD (6) profiles nicely here at this trip.",
